              > 50% of accident-caused pedestrians' injuries happens in intersections. 
            </p>
            <br/>
            <br/>
            <br/>
            <br/>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="column">
        <div class="card is-full-height" style="background-color:#F7F7F7" >
          <p class="card-header-icon">
            <figure class="image is 12x12" style="position: relative; left:10%">

              <img src="../../../static/chat_icon.png" style="width: 75px; height:auto;">

            </figure>
          </p>
      
          <div class="card-content">
            <h1 class="title is-size-5">
              Latest News
            </h1>
            <div class="block"></div>
            <p class="subtitle" style="color:#858482">
