              <img src="../../../static/location_icon.png" style="width: 75px; height:auto;">

            </figure>
          </p>
      
          <div class="card-content">
            <h1 class="title is-size-5">
              About Vision Zero
            </h1>
            <div class="block"></div>
            <p class="subtitle" style="color:#858482">
              In the City of New York, we recognize that deaths and serious injuries in traffic are not inevitable "accidents," but preventable crashes that can be ended through engineering, enforcement, and education.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="section">
    <div class="column">
      <div class="card is-full-height" style="background-color:#F7F7F7" >
        <div class="card-content">
          <h1 class="title is-size-5">
            Project general description
          </h1>
          <div class="block"></div>
          <p class="subtitle" style="color:#858482">
            Vision Zero is a movement known internationally that aims to eliminate the number of fatalities and life-threatening injuries in car accidents. Focusing on the traffic conditions in NYC, our team will build an interactive route planning website with enhanced safety features based on NYPD accident statistics. The website will alert all en route dangerous intersections and, possibly, do personalized routing. For example, if one user uses a wheelchair, our routing will avoid intersections that are dangerous to wheelchair users according to historical accident data.         
          </p>
